com.capgemini.cobigen.api.to

Class HealthCheckReport

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.capgemini.cobigen.api.to.HealthCheckReport

  • public class HealthCheckReport
extends Object
    This is the report created while running the HealthCheck. It contains information such as thrown exceptions or the current configuration and its version. All important information about the HealthCheck can be accessed from here.
